document.title: Dictionary of Contemporary Dutch
document.intro: The Algemeen Nederlands Woordenboek (ANW, Dictionary of Contemporary Dutch) is a corpus-based, scholarly dictionary of contemporary standard Dutch in the Netherlands and in Flanders, describing the Dutch vocabulary from 1970 onwards. The dictionary provides information on form, content ...
